title: Rug Dr. Cleaning
description: A step by step process on how to clean with your Rug Doctor.

asset.author: Rug Doctor LLC
asset.description: A step by step process on how to clean with your Rug Doctor.

transcripts: Roll your rug doctor to the starting spot and adjust the handle to a comfortable position. Turn the switch the carpet then press down on the red button and pull the rug doctor back. The rug doctor cleans the fibers of your carpet on the backward stroke and you'll see dirty water coming up through the see-through dome when you hit the end of the stroke release the red button and pull back about six more inches. Tilt your rug doctor back and roll it forward like a dolly to the next starting position and start again. Keep going until you're done. [Music]
